<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<ScrollView

    android:id="@+id/activity_main"

    xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"

    xmlns:tools="http://schemas.android.com/tools"

    android:layout_width="match_parent"

    android:layout_height="match_parent"
    android:background="@color/colorPrimaryDark"
    tools:context="com.lokesh.interviewprep.HomeActivity"
    xmlns:app="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res-auto">

    <LinearLayout
        android:orientation="vertical"
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="match_parent">

        <RelativeLayout
            android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
            android:layout_marginLeft="24dp"
            android:layout_marginRight="20dp"
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content">
            <TextView
                android:text="Role of Engineers in Disaster Management"
                android:textStyle="bold"
                android:textColor="#FFFF"
                android:textSize="30sp"
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>

        </RelativeLayout>
        <GridLayout
            android:columnCount="1"
            android:rowCount="4"
            android:alignmentMode="alignMargins"
            android:columnOrderPreserved="false"
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content">





            <android.support.v7.widget.CardView
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:layout_columnWeight="1"
                android:layout_rowWeight="1"
                app:cardElevation="6dp"
                app:cardCornerRadius="12dp"
                android:layout_margin="12dp">

                <LinearLayout
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent"
                    android:layout_gravity="center"
                    android:orientation="vertical"
                    android:padding="6dp">

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="match_parent"
                        android:layout_height="match_parent"
                        android:text="Answer #1:-"
                        android:textColor="@color/colorPrimary"
                        android:textSize="20sp"
                        android:textStyle="bold"/>
                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:text="Engineers play a vital role in disaster management.

\n\nAs you know engineers working at weather forecasting centers inform us about the movement of natural calamities. They are providing necessary information after that government bodies take required actions in order to avoid the disaster upto a maximum possible extent.

\n\nEngineers are also the key people after the disaster because after disaster a lot of damage might occur in that region which are rectified by the engineers like electricity problem by electrical engineer and railways track by mechanical engineer and construction works by civil engineer and so many things.

\n\nHence Engineers are the persons who make it possible for the people to live a healthy lifestyle after the disaster also."
                        android:textSize="16sp"/>





                </LinearLayout>
            </android.support.v7.widget.CardView>

            <android.support.v7.widget.CardView
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:layout_columnWeight="1"
                android:layout_rowWeight="1"
                app:cardElevation="6dp"
                app:cardCornerRadius="12dp"
                android:layout_margin="12dp">

                <LinearLayout
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent"
                    android:layout_gravity="center"
                    android:orientation="vertical"
                    android:padding="6dp">

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="match_parent"
                        android:layout_height="match_parent"
                        android:text="Answer #2:-"
                        android:textColor="@color/colorPrimary"
                        android:textSize="20sp"
                        android:textStyle="bold"/>
                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:text="Engineers are most important persons in our life.\n Without engineer we can not survive. Engineers make many types development for society.\n Engineers make a powerful wearing capacity by his technology. Engineers working way different another persons.\n His thoughts, thinking and imagination power are very different. Then I can say by full confidence. If without technology engineer can be survive but without engineers technology can not be survive."
                        android:textSize="16sp"/>





                </LinearLayout>
            </android.support.v7.widget.CardView>

            <android.support.v7.widget.CardView
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:layout_columnWeight="1"
                android:layout_rowWeight="1"
                app:cardElevation="6dp"
                app:cardCornerRadius="12dp"
                android:layout_margin="12dp">

                <LinearLayout
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent"
                    android:layout_gravity="center"
                    android:orientation="vertical"
                    android:padding="6dp">

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="match_parent"
                        android:layout_height="match_parent"
                        android:text="Answer #3:-"
                        android:textColor="@color/colorPrimary"
                        android:textSize="20sp"
                        android:textStyle="bold"/>
                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:text=" Engineers are the boon to the society. They can either make or break a society. They are the ones who can turn our vision into reality. Engineers can design and develop products, they can pave new ways to reach people everyone around the world, they can invent almost anything they want to and their role in disaster affected regions is huge.\n They should come up with solutions that are free because people won't be able to afford in such times of disaster. \nEngineers working in the corporate sector should volunteer in those disaster affected regions as part of their social responsibility and come to their relief. \nImplementing various tools they can come up with solutions that would rather prevent such disasters from happening in the near future."
                        android:textSize="16sp"/>





                </LinearLayout>
            </android.support.v7.widget.CardView>


            <android.support.v7.widget.CardView
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:layout_columnWeight="1"
                android:layout_rowWeight="1"
                app:cardElevation="6dp"
                app:cardCornerRadius="12dp"
                android:layout_margin="12dp">

                <LinearLayout
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent"
                    android:layout_gravity="center"
                    android:orientation="vertical"
                    android:padding="6dp">

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="match_parent"
                        android:layout_height="match_parent"
                        android:text="Answer #4:-"
                        android:textColor="@color/colorPrimary"
                        android:textSize="20sp"
                        android:textStyle="bold"/>
                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:text="Engineers are very important for our society and also for everyone. They covert their imagination in to reality.\n Today what we are achieve somewhere gifted by engeener.\n Like we save our time by using metro train during journey it means somewhere we have to say thanks to engineers who save time by making metro train and we utilize that saving time for our other work. Today engineers give us earthquake proof building which save our life from huge earthquake. Their vast imagine towards mankind proof their importance in society. In kedarnath disaster it wouldn't be possible to save people by man power. But it was engineering who not save the thousands of people but also provide them shelter in short span of time."
                        android:textSize="16sp"/>





                </LinearLayout>
            </android.support.v7.widget.CardView>


            <android.support.v7.widget.CardView
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:layout_columnWeight="1"
                android:layout_rowWeight="1"
                app:cardElevation="6dp"
                app:cardCornerRadius="12dp"
                android:layout_margin="12dp">

                <LinearLayout
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent"
                    android:layout_gravity="center"
                    android:orientation="vertical"
                    android:padding="6dp">

                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="match_parent"
                        android:layout_height="match_parent"
                        android:text="Answer #5:-"
                        android:textColor="@color/colorPrimary"
                        android:textSize="20sp"
                        android:textStyle="bold"/>
                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:text="We can already see that Engineers are playing an important role in disaster management. Engineers specialized in different fields implementing their knowledge to predict the danger before. Environment and weather engineers are working on weather forecasting and analyzing this to get the probability of any climatic conditions that can happen in future thereby warning the people about the destruction that can happen and how to control the situation. \nEngineers also get the impact of earthquakes, and it's intensity over the region. Astronomical Engineers are also analyzing the rotation of the earth and things happening on the planetary level.

\n\nSo, Engineers are doing great jobs in preventing the disaster from happening, thereby reducing the loss that can occur by these disasters."
                        android:textSize="16sp"/>


                </LinearLayout>
            </android.support.v7.widget.CardView>


            <android.support.v7.widget.CardView
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:layout_columnWeight="1"
                android:layout_rowWeight="1"
                app:cardElevation="6dp"
                app:cardCornerRadius="12dp"
                android:layout_margin="12dp">

                <LinearLayout
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent"
                    android:layout_gravity="center"
                    android:orientation="vertical"
                    android:padding="6dp">

                    <Button
                        android:id="@+id/currentlinka7"
                        android:layout_width="match_parent"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:text="for more answers  >"
                        style="?android:attr/borderlessButtonStyle"/>


                </LinearLayout>
            </android.support.v7.widget.CardView>








        </GridLayout>


    </LinearLayout>


</ScrollView>